{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2d11ee8942","title":"反磨擦斗争必须注意自卫原则叫","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"758cd16394","index":0,"year":1940,"month":3,"day":14,"articleId":"2d11ee8942"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f16f0144e3","type":"paragraph","text":"反磨擦斗争必须注意自卫原则叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"2d11ee8942"},{"id":"04574d970a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年3月14日）朱、彭、杨，刘、邓，左、黄，陈、罗，徐、朱（甲）反磨擦斗争必须注意自卫原则，不应超出自卫的范围，如果超出这个范围，则对全国的影响和统一战线是很不利的。尤其对中央军应注意此点，因国共合作主要就是同中央军的合作。（乙）目前山西、河北的反磨擦斗争即须告一段落，不应再行发展。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"2d11ee8942"},{"id":"9c9e3a14db","type":"paragraph","text":"中央书记处及军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"2d11ee8942"},{"id":"65bb4f210c","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十四日口这是毛泽东为中共中央书记处和中央军委起草给朱德、彭德怀、插","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"2d11ee8942"}],"page":{"id":"0c94b817c5","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"2d11ee8942","start":476,"end":476}}}},"__N_SSG":true}